This is a large database application that was programmed with: PostgreSQL, PostGIS, HTML, CSS, JavaScript and Java.  
The program was developed to visualize crime data in the city of Chicago.
The application supports: querying, digitizing, custom choropleth mapping, spatio-temporal animation and statistical analysis.

Important Files
main.html; the main landing page
addRecord.jsp; call to add new point to database
aniimation.jsp; handles call to database for temporal animation 
callQuery.jsp; for basic query, returns points for a specific type of crime
callQueryDate.jsp; similar to callQuery but it looks for records in a defined period of time
choropleth.jsp; handles the call to make the custom choropleth map
